CSE508: Network Security, Spring 2016
Homework 2 Solution (by Emaad Ahmed Manzoor, 110622899)
--------------------------------------------------------

Compile
-------

  make

Test
----

  - From a file

      - Without BPF or string filtering:          make test-file
      - With BPF filtering, no string filtering:  make test-file-expr
      - With BPF and string filtering:            make test-file-string

  - From an ethernet interface (without BPF or string filtering)

      - On Linux:                                 make test-eth0
      - On OSX/FreeBSD:                           make test-eth0-osx 

Files
-----

  - README              This file.
  - Makefile            Used to compile and test the sniffer.
  - ethernet.h, ip.h    structs for ethernet and IP headers.
  - param.h             Miscelleanous parameters.
  - main.c              Main code.

References
----------

  http://www.tcpdump.org/pcap.html
